Student Organizations     Search the site     Toggle Menu      Search                  Student Organizations      LOGICA   Main Menu    Members    Get Involved           Calendar         Contact Us     Eyebrow menu    UIC College of Engineering Home    UIC menu    UIC.edu    Campus Map       Search                LOGICA                LOGICA  Latinx Organization for Growth in Computing and Academics                   Our Mission    Increasing the participation and success of students from Latinx and underrepresented communities pursuing careers in the field of computing and computer science. We are a network of students working together to develop technical, leadership, and professional skills through an environment that encourages camaraderie and growth not only as an individual, but as a community. We are an organization dedicated to inclusivity and welcome all who share our vision.
